# gasMonitor

气体遥测监测预警平台

部署注意事项:<br />

- application.yml配置中修改数据库连接url、用户名、密码
- url.js中修改前端请求后端的url
- 菜单、角色、用户表、系统配置表的初始化

版本包更新后常见问题：  
- 页面无法访问，检查配置信息，确认tomcat log确认服务正常运行
- 页面部分元素无法加载，清空浏览器缓存

   
Mysql建库与建表、初始化数据:
```
1、创建数据库gasMonitor
使用Navicat客户端工具创建gasMonitor数据库；
或者使用终端执行sql：
mysql>create datebase gasMonitor;


2、建立表结构及初始化数据
使用Navicat客户端工具进入gasMonitor的Query界面，执行如下语句：


SET NAMES utf8mb4;

-- ----------------------------
-- Table structure for g_menu
-- ----------------------------
DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `g_menu`;
CREATE TABLE `g_menu`  (
  `id` varchar(50) CHARACTER SET utf8mb4 COLLATE utf8mb4_general_ci NOT NULL COMMENT '菜单ID',
  `menu_name` varchar(100) CHARACTER SET utf8mb4 COLLATE utf8mb4_general_ci NOT NULL COMMENT '菜单名称',
  `menu_type` varchar(10) CHARACTER SET utf8mb4 COLLATE utf8mb4_general_ci NOT NULL DEFAULT '' COMMENT '菜单类型',
  `menu_parent_id` varchar(50) CHARACTER SET utf8mb4 COLLATE utf8mb4_general_ci NOT NULL DEFAULT '0' COMMENT '父菜单ID 0-顶级',
  `sort_num` int(10) UNSIGNED NOT NULL DEFAULT 0 COMMENT '显示顺序',
  `path` varchar(200) CHARACTER SET utf8mb4 COLLATE utf8mb4_general_ci NULL DEFAULT '' COMMENT '菜单路由地址',
  `icon` varchar(50) CHARACTER SET utf8mb4 COLLATE utf8mb4_general_ci NOT NULL DEFAULT '' COMMENT '菜单图标',
  `component` varchar(512) CHARACTER SET utf8mb4 COLLATE utf8mb4_general_ci NULL DEFAULT '' COMMENT '页面组件路径,>分隔可跨级多个',
  `state` varchar(50) CHARACTER SET utf8mb4 COLLATE utf8mb4_general_ci NOT NULL DEFAULT '0' COMMENT '菜单状态',
  `del_flag` varchar(50) CHARACTER SET utf8mb4 COLLATE utf8mb4_general_ci NOT NULL DEFAULT '0' COMMENT '删除标志',
  `remarks` varchar(255) CHARACTER SET utf8mb4 COLLATE utf8mb4_general_ci NULL DEFAULT '' COMMENT '备注',
  `level` int(10) NOT NULL COMMENT '层级',
  `createBy` varchar(64) CHARACTER SET utf8mb4 COLLATE utf8mb4_general_ci NULL DEFAULT '' COMMENT '创建者',
  `modifyBy` varchar(64) CHARACTER SET utf8mb4 COLLATE utf8mb4_general_ci NULL DEFAULT '' COMMENT '最后修改者',
  `createTime` datetime(0) NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP(0) COMMENT '创建时间',
  `modifyTime` datetime(0) NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP(0) ON UPDATE CURRENT_TIMESTAMP(0) COMMENT '修改时间',
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`) USING BTREE
) ENGINE = InnoDB CHARACTER SET = utf8mb4 COLLATE = utf8mb4_general_ci COMMENT = '菜单权限表' ROW_FORMAT = Dynamic;

-- Table structure for g_role
-- ----------------------------
DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `g_role`;
CREATE TABLE `g_role`  (
  `id` varchar(50) CHARACTER SET utf8mb4 COLLATE utf8mb4_general_ci NOT NULL COMMENT '主键ID',
  `role_name` varchar(100) CHARACTER SET utf8mb4 COLLATE utf8mb4_general_ci NOT NULL DEFAULT '' COMMENT '角色名称',
  `role_key` varchar(64) CHARACTER SET utf8mb4 COLLATE utf8mb4_general_ci NULL DEFAULT '' COMMENT '角色标识key',
  `state` varchar(50) CHARACTER SET utf8mb4 COLLATE utf8mb4_general_ci NULL DEFAULT '0' COMMENT '状态',
  `sort_num` int(4) NOT NULL DEFAULT 0 COMMENT '显示顺序',
  `del_flag` varchar(50) CHARACTER SET utf8mb4 COLLATE utf8mb4_general_ci NOT NULL DEFAULT '0' COMMENT '删除标志',
  `remarks` varchar(255) CHARACTER SET utf8mb4 COLLATE utf8mb4_general_ci NULL DEFAULT '' COMMENT '备注',
  `menu_id_list` varchar(1000) CHARACTER SET utf8mb4 COLLATE utf8mb4_general_ci NULL DEFAULT NULL COMMENT '菜单id集合',
  `createBy` varchar(64) CHARACTER SET utf8mb4 COLLATE utf8mb4_general_ci NULL DEFAULT '' COMMENT '创建者',
  `modifyBy` varchar(64) CHARACTER SET utf8mb4 COLLATE utf8mb4_general_ci NULL DEFAULT '' COMMENT '最后修改者',
  `createTime` datetime(0) NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP(0) COMMENT '创建时间',
  `modifyTime` datetime(0) NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP(0) ON UPDATE CURRENT_TIMESTAMP(0) COMMENT '修改时间',
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`) USING BTREE,
  INDEX `idx_role_name`(`role_name`) USING BTREE
) ENGINE = InnoDB CHARACTER SET = utf8mb4 COLLATE = utf8mb4_general_ci COMMENT = '角色信息表' ROW_FORMAT = Dynamic;

-- ----------------------------
-- Table structure for g_user
-- ----------------------------
DROP TABLE IF EXISTS `g_user`;
CREATE TABLE `g_user`  (
  `id` varchar(50) CHARACTER SET utf8mb4 COLLATE utf8mb4_general_ci NOT NULL COMMENT 'id',
  `user_name` varchar(255) CHARACTER SET utf8mb4 COLLATE utf8mb4_general_ci NOT NULL DEFAULT '' COMMENT '用户登录名',
  `password` varchar(255) CHARACTER SET utf8mb4 COLLATE utf8mb4_general_ci NOT NULL DEFAULT '' COMMENT '密码',
  `real_name` varchar(100) CHARACTER SET utf8mb4 COLLATE utf8mb4_general_ci NULL DEFAULT '' COMMENT '真实姓名',
  `phone` varchar(32) CHARACTER SET utf8mb4 COLLATE utf8mb4_general_ci NULL DEFAULT '' COMMENT '手机号码',
  `email` varchar(255) CHARACTER SET utf8mb4 COLLATE utf8mb4_general_ci NULL DEFAULT '' COMMENT '邮箱',
  `type` varchar(50) CHARACTER SET utf8mb4 COLLATE utf8mb4_general_ci NOT NULL DEFAULT '0' COMMENT '类型',
  `last_login_time` datetime(0) NULL DEFAULT NULL COMMENT '最后登录时间',
  `del_flag` varchar(50) CHARACTER SET utf8mb4 COLLATE utf8mb4_general_ci NOT NULL DEFAULT '0' COMMENT '删除标志',
  `remarks` varchar(255) CHARACTER SET utf8mb4 COLLATE utf8mb4_general_ci NULL DEFAULT '' COMMENT '备注',
  `role_key` varchar(50) CHARACTER SET utf8mb4 COLLATE utf8mb4_general_ci NOT NULL COMMENT '角色key',
  `createBy` varchar(50) CHARACTER SET utf8mb4 COLLATE utf8mb4_general_ci NULL DEFAULT '' COMMENT '创建者',
  `modifyBy` varchar(50) CHARACTER SET utf8mb4 COLLATE utf8mb4_general_ci NULL DEFAULT '' COMMENT '最后修改者',
  `createTime` datetime(0) NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP(0) COMMENT '创建时间',
  `modifyTime` datetime(0) NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP(0) ON UPDATE CURRENT_TIMESTAMP(0) COMMENT '修改时间',
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`) USING BTREE,
  INDEX `idx_username`(`user_name`) USING BTREE,
  INDEX `idx_phone`(`phone`) USING BTREE,
  INDEX `idx_email`(`email`) USING BTREE
) ENGINE = InnoDB CHARACTER SET = utf8mb4 COLLATE = utf8mb4_general_ci COMMENT = '用户表' ROW_FORMAT = Dynamic;
```
